    {
      "parameters": {
        "toRecipients": "={{322882755__items[]column_values[]text}}",
        "subject": "Request for AWR Information – {{322665531__candidate__firstName}} {{322665531__candidate__lastName}} ({{322665531__jobOrder__title}}",
        "bodyContent": "=<p>\n    Dear Talentia Group,\n</p>\n<p>\n    In line with our responsibilities under the <strong>Agency Workers Regulations (AWR)</strong>, we are required to confirm that temporary workers engaged through your agency receive fair and equal treatment when compared with permanent employees in similar roles at Propeller Pay.\n</p>\n<p>\n    &nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n    To support this process, we kindly ask you to complete <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://form.jotform.com/252642929776068?workerName={{322665531__candidate__firstName}} {{322665531__candidate__lastName}}&amp;jobTitle={{322665531__jobOrder__title}}&amp;mondayid={{322791377__items[]id}}\">this form</a> with details of the comparable permanent position for <strong>{{322665531__candidate__firstName}} {{322665531__candidate__lastName}}, {{322665531__jobOrder__title}}</strong>.&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n    &nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n    If there is no directly comparable permanent role, please complete the form accordingly.&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n    &nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n    We would appreciate it if the details could be completed and returned at your earliest convenience. Should you have any questions or need further clarification, please do not hesitate to contact us.\n</p>\n<p>\n    &nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n    Thank you for your assistance in helping us remain compliant with AWR and ensuring fair treatment for workers.\n</p>\n<p>\n    &nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n    Kind regards,<br>\n    <strong>Propeller Pay</strong>\n</p>",
        "additionalFields": {}
      },
